<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>STAND BEFORE THE KING</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpen angah ding hitiu,
 Angelte tawh lasa'i tiu;
 Dantak leh dantak leh,
 Luigal nuomah leng hitiu;
 Kumsawta Amah pakin,
 Dantak leh, dantak leh.

[V2]
 Lalpen angah ding hitiu,
 Angelte tawh lasa'i tiu;
 I Lalpen chuh lopi hen,
 Hallelujah, Hallejah,
 Lalpen angah ding hitiu.

[V3]
 2. Tum un van dak haw tum un,
 Lalpen angah ding hitiu;
 Dantak leh, dantak leh,
 Ziechun lungkham bei ta'n a;
 A min chuh chawian hitiu,
 Dantak leh, dantak leh.

[V4]
 3. Tho in, ka tha chawian in,
 Lalpen angah ding inla;
 Dantak leh, dantak leh,
 Na go phapen Amah pie'n;
 Amah bangin um inla,
 Dantak leh, dantak leh.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>369</hymn_number>
</song>